AS SET NOCOUNT ON BEGIN
SELECT [BARRONS_INDICATOR_CODE] AS BarronsIndexCode, [BARRONS_INDICATOR_DESCRIPTION] AS BarronsIndexDescrip.on
FROM [MCRISS].[USMC].[BARRONS_INDICATORS] ORDER BY BARRONS_INDICATOR_CODE END
